PN,39101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772705111
OL,3,CVigil held for Iran's Khamenei as
OL,4,Ccounter-protesters gather nearby
OL,6,FProtestors and counter-protestors have
OL,7,Fheld a "peaceful" demonstration in
OL,8,Frelation to the ongoing conflict
OL,9,Fbetween the US, Israel and Iran.
OL,11,FThe event began as a vigil
OL,12,Fcommemorating the Supreme Leader of
OL,13,FIran, Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, in
OL,14,FManchester, with two sides separated
OL,15,Fby a heavy uniformed police presence.
OL,17,FThe former Iran leader, a lone target
OL,18,Fof the US and Israel, was killed
OL,19,Fduring coordinated daytime strikes on
OL,20,FTehran on Saturday, 28 February.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
