FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772705111
OL,3,CVigil held for Iran's Khamenei as
OL,4,Ccounter-protesters gather nearby
OL,6,FUp to 100 people, some carrying flags
OL,7,Fof the current regime, gathered on
OL,8,FSydney Street, off Oxford Road, where
OL,9,Fa handwritten sign read: "You can kill
OL,10,Fa man but you can't kill an ideology".
OL,12,FPropped up on a table, shrouded in a
OL,13,Fblack cloth was another sign next to
OL,14,Fphotograph of the Ayatollah which
OL,15,Fread: "My enemies have the support of
OL,16,Feach other to kill me, O Heart warming
OL,17,Flove.
OL,19,F"I have only your support, loyal to
OL,20,FAyatollah Khamenei".
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@eO]wD@GOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
