OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772705111
OL,3,CVigil held for Iran's Khamenei as
OL,4,Ccounter-protesters gather nearby
OL,6,FA printed message was also displayed
OL,7,Fon the table which read "we believe,
OL,8,Ftrust, admire the revolution". A
OL,9,Fposter for the vigil said it was
OL,10,Fsupported by the Friends of Islamic
OL,11,FCentre of Manchester.
OL,13,FThe street, in the university area,
OL,14,Fwas closed off to traffic and a large
OL,15,Fnumber of police kept the groups apart.
OL,17,FIn contrast, up to 300 to 400 counter-
OL,18,Fprotesters turned out for a much more
OL,19,Fjubilant event, with demonstrators
OL,20,Fcarrying flags of Israel, Britain and
OL,21,Fthe old Iranian flag.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@]O]
