PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772705111
OL,3,CVigil held for Iran's Khamenei as
OL,4,Ccounter-protesters gather nearby
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Chris Sykes
OL,7,Fsaid in an earlier statement: "The
OL,8,Fevents in the Middle East are
OL,9,Fsignificant for those in Greater
OL,10,FManchester with ties to Iran and the
OL,11,Fwider region.
OL,13,F"It is understandable that these evoke
OL,14,Fa range of views and emotions."We are
OL,15,Faware of plans for a vigil and a
OL,16,Fnearby counter-protest in the city
OL,17,Fcentre on Wednesday night.
OL,19,F"We are engaging with those involved
OL,20,Fas well as our partners at Manchester
OL,21,FCity Council."
OL,26,@oD@_OUuD@AOUvD@_OU{D@AOU}D@NO]
