PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772705111
OL,3,CVigil held for Iran's Khamenei as
OL,4,Ccounter-protesters gather nearby
OL,6,FHe said Greater Manchester Police had
OL,7,Freceived assurances from both sides
OL,8,Fthat they intended the vigil and the
OL,9,Fcounter-protest to "remain peaceful".
